
Instructions on how to log in when running the app….

All you need is a user ID.Existing user “bd” has traded a lot.
 Also “ll” and “kh” have done some trading. “tt” and “bb” also exist.
 If you enter a user ID that doesn't exist you are led to a form where
  you must enter the details for this user. Then the user is added in Firestore


Navigation :
Login->Home  ( if id = bd )
Login->Signin
Signin->Home
Home->Search
Home->Stock
Home->Portfolio
Account->PuppyAttack
Account->Settings
Account->History
Search->Stock
Stock->Trading

All->Back
All->Search
All->Notifications
All->Account